theorem interior_closure_inter_closure_eq_inter_interior_closure
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} :
    interior (closure A ∩ closure B) =
      interior (closure A) ∩ interior (closure B) := by
  ext x
  constructor
  · intro hx
    have hxA : x ∈ interior (closure A) :=
      (interior_mono (Set.inter_subset_left :
        (closure A ∩ closure B : Set X) ⊆ closure A)) hx
    have hxB : x ∈ interior (closure B) :=
      (interior_mono (Set.inter_subset_right :
        (closure A ∩ closure B : Set X) ⊆ closure B)) hx
    exact And.intro hxA hxB
  · rintro ⟨hxA, hxB⟩
    rcases mem_interior.1 hxA with ⟨U, hUopen, hUx, hUsub⟩
    rcases mem_interior.1 hxB with ⟨V, hVopen, hVx, hVsub⟩
    have hWopen : IsOpen (U ∩ V) := hUopen.inter hVopen
    have hWsub : (U ∩ V : Set X) ⊆ closure A ∩ closure B := by
      intro y hy
      exact And.intro (hUsub hy.1) (hVsub hy.2)
    have hxW : x ∈ U ∩ V := And.intro hUx hVx
    exact mem_interior.2 ⟨U ∩ V, hWopen, hxW, hWsub⟩

theorem inter_subset_closure_left_right {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {U V A B : Set X} (hU : U ⊆ closure A) (hV : V ⊆ closure B) :
    (U ∩ V : Set X) ⊆ closure A ∩ closure B := by
  intro x hx
  exact And.intro (hU hx.1) (hV hx.2)
